Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: invalidAPIKey
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: Given apiKey is invalid. You can get it from https://app.qualaroo.com/dashboard by tapping on Setup when you expand selected site/application.

Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: noSurvey
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: There is no active survey with given name or it was corrupted.

Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: invalidSiteId
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: Paramether siteId should be non-empty String with only digits.

Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: dataEncodingException
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: Problem occured while using data(using: String.Encoding) function.

Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: languageCodeInvalid
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: Language code must be type of string with exactly two letters.

Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: alreadySeenOrFinished
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: There is survey with that alias but user already seen it or finished it, and it shouldn’t be shown again or it’s to soon to display it.

Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.name: noInternet
Classes/Qualaroo/SDKError.html#/s:8Quala.abstract: There is no access to web right now.

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC6sh.name: shared
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC6sh.abstract: Instance of Qualaroo class that should be used.

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC9co.name: configure(withApiKey:autotracking:)
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC9co.abstract: You need to call this method on Qualaroo.shared to create and configure main component with given credentials

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC27s.name: setPreferredSurveysLanguage(_:)
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC27s.abstract: Set dafault language that you want to use for surveys. If survey won’t support preferred language it will try to use english, if it’s also not supported then it will use first one from supported languages.

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC7se.name: setLogo(_:)
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC7se.abstract: Set default theme you want to use for surveys. You can create your own one or use one of predefined be calling Theme.withStyle(_:logo:).

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC9se.name: setUserID(_:)
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC9se.abstract: Way to identify user. This ID will be sent with every response user gave us. Can be changed between surveys. We still will send same device unique ID, for every response given from this device.

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC18r.name: removeUserProperty(_:)
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC18r.abstract: Remove userProperty if there is one. If there is no property with given key nothing happens.

Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC10s.name: showSurvey(with:on:)
Classes/Qualaroo.html#/s:8QualarooAAC10s.abstract: Way to show survey with selected name (alias).
